==Mandarin==

===Pronunciation===
[[Pinyin]]: yī shēng shòu yòng bù jìn

===Phrase===
'''[[一]][[生]][[受]][[用]][[不]][[尽]]''' ([[Simplified Chinese]])

# (''idiom'') Reap the benefits of something for the rest of one's life.

#: ''[[他]][[当年]][[对]][[我]][[的]][[一番]][[教导]]，[[让]][[我]]'''一生受用不尽'''.'' ([[Simplified Chinese]])

#: ''[[他]][[當年]][[對]][[我]][[的]][[一番]][[教導]]，[[讓]][[我]]'''一生受用不盡'''.'' ([[Traditional Chinese]])

===Alternate forms===
[[一]][[生]][[受]][[用]][[不]][[盡]] ([[Traditional Chinese]])

